{"tha-ap498:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap498:0.2":"Kinkanipupphavagga ","tha-ap498:0.3":"Ghatamandadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap498:1.1":"“Sucintitam bhagavantam, ","tha-ap498:1.2":"lokajettham narasabham; ","tha-ap498:1.3":"Upavittham maharannam, ","tha-ap498:1.4":"vatabadhena pilitam. ","tha-ap498:2.1":"Disva cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap498:2.2":"ghatamandamupanayim; ","tha-ap498:2.3":"Katatta acitatta ca, ","tha-ap498:2.4":"ganga bhagirathi ayam. ","tha-ap498:3.1":"Mahasamudda cattaro, ","tha-ap498:3.2":"ghatam sampajjare mama; ","tha-ap498:3.3":"Ayanca pathavi ghora, ","tha-ap498:3.4":"appamana asankhiya. ","tha-ap498:4.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap498:4.2":"bhavate madhusakkara; ","tha-ap498:4.3":"Catuddipa ime rukkha, ","tha-ap498:4.4":"padapa dharaniruha. ","tha-ap498:5.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap498:5.2":"kapparukkha bhavanti te; ","tha-ap498:5.3":"Pannasakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap498:5.4":"devarajjamakarayim. ","tha-ap498:6.1":"Ekapannasakkhattunca, ","tha-ap498:6.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap498:6.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap498:6.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap498:7.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap498:7.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap498:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap498:7.4":"ghatamandassidam phalam. ","tha-ap498:8.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap498:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap498:8.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap498:9.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap498:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap498:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap498:10.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap498:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap498:10.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap498:11.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ghatamandadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap498:12.1":"Ghatamandadayakattherassapadanam chattham. "}